result:
<st-modal
  title="次卡扣费规则设置"
  v-model="show"
  @ok="postGlobalSetting"
  size="small"
>
  <a-radio-group v-model="charge_type">
    <a-radio
      :class="bPage('radio')"
      v-for="(item, index) in rule"
      :key="index"
      :value="item.value"
    >
      <st-input-number
        :min="1"
        :max="24"
        style="width:50px;"
        v-model="charge_value"
        v-if="item.value === PAY_RULE.HOUR"
      />
      {{ item.label }}
    </a-radio>
  </a-radio-group>
</st-modal>
